This module is demo.lambdamatchbind.

Define User with id, name.

To greetUser with user, prefix, produce:
  Let f be function with value, produce:
    Match value:
      When User(id, name), Return Text.concat(prefix, name).
      When other, Return prefix.
  Return f(user).

To posOrZero with count, produce:
  Let sel be function with value, produce:
    If value greater than 0:
      Return value.
    Otherwise:
      Return 0.
  Return sel(count).
